        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "因為知道這等人已經背道，犯了罪，自己明知不是，還是去做。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "knowing that such a man is perverted and is sinning, being self-condemned."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You may be sure that such people are warped and sinful; they are self-condemned."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "For people like that have turned away from the truth, and their own sins condemn them."
      }
    },
